amrwbparse

amrwbparse — Adaptive Multi-Rate WideBand audio parser

Synopsis




                    GstAmrwbParse;

Object Hierarchy


  GObject
   +----GstObject
         +----GstElement
               +----GstAmrwbParse

Description

This is an AMR wideband parser.

Example launch line

gst-launch filesrc location=abc.amr ! amrwbparse ! amrwbdec ! audioresample ! audioconvert ! alsasink

Element Information
